claim.claim-text:
The electronic management system for vehicle according to one of claims 6 or 7, characterized in that the internal communication means (10a, 10b, 10c) comprise at least one of the following antennas:
- an antenna located in a front part of the passenger compartment (10a);
- an antenna located in a median part of the passenger compartment (10b);
- an antenna located in a rear part of the passenger compartment (10c).
